msgid "About WMAA"
msgstr "关于西澳多元文化援助联盟"

msgid "WMAA is an ACNC-registered charity dedicated to supporting culturally and linguistically diverse (CALD) communities across Western Australia. We provide practical help, cultural understanding, and support for migrants, students, visitors, and families in need."
msgstr "WMAA是一家经ACNC注册的慈善机构，致力于支持西澳大利亚各地文化和语言多元化（CALD）社区。我们为有需要的移民、学生、访客和家庭提供实际帮助、文化理解和支持。"

msgid "We work collaboratively with universities, community organisations, service providers, and government agencies to build a strong support network for CALD individuals."
msgstr "我们与大学、社区组织、服务提供商和政府机构合作，为CALD个人建立强大的支持网络。"

msgid "Registered Charity"
msgstr "注册慈善机构"

msgid "Communities Served"
msgstr "服务社区"

msgid "Our Vision"
msgstr "我们的愿景"

msgid "To build a resilient, connected, and empowered multicultural community in Western Australia where everyone has access to support in their time of need."
msgstr "在西澳大利亚建立一个具有韧性、紧密联系且充满活力的多元文化社区，让每个人在需要时都能获得支持。"

msgid "What Drives Us"
msgstr "我们的驱动力"

msgid "Our Vision & Values"
msgstr "我们的愿景与价值观"

msgid "Compassion"
msgstr "同理心"

msgid "Treating every person with dignity and care."
msgstr "以尊重和关怀对待每一个人。"

msgid "Cultural Respect"
msgstr "文化尊重"

msgid "Honouring the diversity of all backgrounds."
msgstr "尊重所有背景的多样性。"

msgid "Community"
msgstr "社区"

msgid "Stronger together through collaboration."
msgstr "通过合作共同变得更强大。"

msgid "How We Work"
msgstr "我们的工作方式"

msgid "Our Approach"
msgstr "我们的方法"

msgid "Our services are both proactive and responsive."
msgstr "我们的服务既主动出击，又快速响应。"

msgid "Providing immediate crisis assistance, housing referrals, and advocacy."
msgstr "提供即时危机援助、住房转介和权益倡导。"

msgid "Delivering education and awareness programs that prevent harm and build resilience."
msgstr "提供预防伤害和增强韧性的教育和意识提升项目。"

msgid "Acting as cultural mediators to bridge communication gaps between families, services, and authorities."
msgstr "作为文化调解员，弥合家庭、服务机构和当局之间的沟通鸿沟。"

msgid "The Future"
msgstr "展望未来"

msgid "Looking Ahead"
msgstr "展望前景"

msgid "WMAA will continue to expand its services by building on these four pillars."
msgstr "WMAA将继续在以下四大支柱的基础上扩展其服务。"

msgid "Strengthening Partnerships"
msgstr "加强合作伙伴关系"

msgid "Collaborating with local and international organisations to expand our reach and improve support for CALD communities."
msgstr "与本地和国际组织合作，扩大覆盖范围，改善对CALD社区的支持。"

msgid "Raising Community Awareness"
msgstr "提升社区意识"

msgid "Promoting greater understanding of available services so individuals know where to turn for help."
msgstr "推广对现有服务的了解，让个人知道在哪里寻求帮助。"

msgid "Building a Skilled Volunteer Network"
msgstr "建立专业志愿者网络"

msgid "Training volunteers in cultural mediation, emergency response, and advocacy to deliver compassionate assistance."
msgstr "培训志愿者掌握文化调解、紧急响应和权益倡导技能，提供富有同情心的援助。"

msgid "Developing Tailored Support Programs"
msgstr "开发定制支持项目"

msgid "Creating specialised initiatives for vulnerable groups, including victims of family violence, fraud, and housing insecurity."
msgstr "为弱势群体创建专项计划，包括家庭暴力受害者、欺诈受害者和住房不稳定人群。"

msgid "Our Organisation"
msgstr "我们的机构"

msgid "Read More"
msgstr "阅读更多"

msgid "WA Multicultural Assistance Alliance"
msgstr "西澳多元文化援助联盟"

msgid "Responding With Compassion, Leading With Purpose"
msgstr "以同理心回应，以使命感引领"

msgid "Partner with WMAA to expand our reach and impact. Together, we can create a stronger, more connected community across Western Australia."
msgstr "与WMAA合作，扩大我们的覆盖范围和影响力。携手共建更强大、更紧密联系的西澳大利亚社区。"

