msgstr "我们的核心服务"

msgid "Crisis Response & Emergency Support"
msgstr "危机响应与紧急援助"

msgid "Immediate assistance for individuals and families in crisis situations."
msgstr "为处于危机中的个人和家庭提供即时援助。"

msgid "Cultural Mediation & Family Liaison"
msgstr "文化调解与家庭联络"

msgid "Bridging cultural and language gaps between families and service providers."
msgstr "弥合家庭与服务提供者之间的文化和语言障碍。"

msgid "Temporary Accommodation Referrals"
msgstr "临时住宿转介"

msgid "Connecting people in hardship with safe short-term housing options."
msgstr "为有困难的人提供安全短期住房选择。"

msgid "Anti-Fraud & Safety Awareness"
msgstr "反诈骗与安全意识"

msgid "Educating community members to protect themselves from scams."
msgstr "教育社区成员保护自己免受诈骗。"

msgid "Health & Welfare Advocacy"
msgstr "健康与福利倡导"

msgid "Helping individuals navigate healthcare and social services fairly."
msgstr "帮助个人公平地获取医疗保健和社会服务。"

msgid "Sustainability"
msgstr "可持续发展"

msgid "Ensuring lasting benefits for communities through long-term programs."
msgstr "通过长期项目确保社区获得持久利益。"

msgid "View All Services"
msgstr "查看所有服务"

msgid "Support Our Mission"
msgstr "支持我们的使命"

msgid "Your donation helps us provide emergency support, cultural mediation, and essential services to CALD communities across WA."
msgstr "您的捐款帮助我们为西澳各地的CALD社区提供紧急支援、文化调解和基本服务。"

msgid "What We Offer"
msgstr "我们提供的服务"

msgid "Our Services"
msgstr "我们的服务"

msgid "Service 01"
msgstr "服务 01"

msgid "Providing immediate assistance to individuals and families in crisis, ensuring access to essential resources and urgent care when it's needed most."
msgstr "为处于危机中的个人和家庭提供即时援助，确保在最需要时获得基本资源和紧急救护。"

msgid "Our crisis team responds rapidly to situations involving housing instability, family breakdown, medical emergencies, and other urgent welfare needs within CALD communities."
msgstr "我们的危机团队快速响应CALD社区中涉及住房不稳定、家庭破裂、医疗紧急情况和其他紧迫福利需求的情况。"

msgid "Get Support"
msgstr "获取支持"

msgid "24/7 emergency referral support"
msgstr "24/7紧急转介支持"

msgid "Coordination with emergency services"
msgstr "与紧急服务机构协调"

msgid "Access to food, clothing & essentials"
msgstr "获取食物、衣物和生活必需品"

msgid "Family crisis counselling referrals"
msgstr "家庭危机辅导转介"

msgid "Safe house and shelter connections"
msgstr "庇护所和避难所连接"

msgid "Service 02"
msgstr "服务 02"

msgid "Bridging cultural and language gaps to help families communicate effectively with service providers, schools, and community organisations."
msgstr "弥合文化和语言障碍，帮助家庭与服务提供商、学校和社区组织有效沟通。"

msgid "Our trained cultural mediators work directly with families, schools, courts, and welfare agencies to ensure every individual is heard and understood."
msgstr "我们训练有素的文化调解员直接与家庭、学校、法院和福利机构合作，确保每个人都能被倾听和理解。"

msgid "Request a Mediator"
msgstr "申请调解员"

msgid "Multilingual mediators available"
msgstr "提供多语言调解员"

msgid "School and education liaison"
msgstr "学校和教育联络"

msgid "Court and legal support facilitation"
msgstr "法庭和法律支持协助"

msgid "Government agency communication"
msgstr "政府机构沟通"

msgid "Family conflict resolution support"
msgstr "家庭冲突解决支持"

msgid "Service 03"
msgstr "服务 03"

msgid "Connecting those experiencing hardship with safe and suitable short-term housing options through our trusted network of partners."
msgstr "通过我们可信赖的合作伙伴网络，为有困难的人提供安全、合适的短期住房选择。"

msgid "We work with shelters, faith communities, and housing providers to ensure no one in our community is left without a safe place to stay."
msgstr "我们与庇护所、宗教社区和住房提供商合作，确保社区中没有人因无处可住而流离失所。"

msgid "Find Housing Help"
msgstr "寻找住房帮助"

msgid "Emergency accommodation referrals"
msgstr "紧急住宿转介"

msgid "Transitional housing connections"
msgstr "过渡性住房联系"

msgid "Culturally appropriate placements"
msgstr "文化适宜的安置"

msgid "Support for families with children"
msgstr "为有孩子的家庭提供支持"

msgid "Ongoing follow-up and welfare checks"
msgstr "持续跟进和福利检查"

msgid "Service 04"
msgstr "服务 04"

msgid "Anti-Fraud & Safety Awareness Programs"
msgstr "反诈骗与安全意识项目"

msgid "Educating community members on protecting themselves from scams, exploitation, and unsafe situations through targeted awareness initiatives."
msgstr "通过有针对性的意识提升活动，教育社区成员如何保护自己免受诈骗、剥削和不安全情况的侵害。"

msgid "CALD communities are often targeted by sophisticated scams. Our programs build awareness and resilience through workshops, resources, and direct outreach."
msgstr "CALD社区经常成为复杂诈骗的目标。我们的项目通过研讨会、资源和直接宣传来提高意识和增强抵御能力。"

msgid "Community fraud awareness workshops"
msgstr "社区反诈骗意识研讨会"

msgid "Online safety and scam education"
msgstr "网络安全和反诈骗教育"

msgid "Financial exploitation prevention"
msgstr "金融诈骗预防"

msgid "Multilingual resources and materials"
msgstr "多语言资源和材料"

msgid "Referral to police and support services"
msgstr "转介至警方和支持服务"

msgid "Service 05"
msgstr "服务 05"

msgid "Supporting individuals in navigating healthcare and social services, ensuring fair access to essential wellbeing and welfare resources."
msgstr "支持个人在医疗保健和社会服务中找到方向，确保公平获取基本健康和福利资源。"

msgid "We advocate for CALD community members within the healthcare system, helping them understand their rights and access the services they are entitled to."
msgstr "我们在医疗保健系统内为CALD社区成员倡导权益，帮助他们了解自己的权利并获得应有的服务。"

msgid "Get Advocacy Support"
msgstr "获取权益支持"

msgid "Hospital and GP navigation support"
msgstr "医院和全科医生导诊支持"

msgid "Mental health service referrals"
msgstr "心理健康服务转介"

msgid "Centrelink and welfare guidance"
msgstr "Centrelink和福利指导"

msgid "NDIS access support"
msgstr "NDIS申请支持"

msgid "Health interpreter coordination"
msgstr "医疗口译员协调"

msgid "Service 06"
msgstr "服务 06"

msgid "Ensuring lasting benefits for communities through programs designed with long-term impact and resilience in mind."
msgstr "通过以长期影响和可持续性为核心设计的项目，确保社区获得持久利益。"

msgid "Our sustainability initiatives focus on empowering communities to support themselves, reducing dependency and building long-term capacity within CALD groups."
msgstr "我们的可持续发展计划专注于赋权社区自我支持，减少依赖性，在CALD群体中建立长期能力。"

msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "参与其中"

msgid "Community capacity building programs"
msgstr "社区能力建设项目"

msgid "Volunteer recruitment and training"
msgstr "志愿者招募和培训"

msgid "Peer support network development"
msgstr "同伴支持网络发展"

msgid "Partnership and funding programs"
msgstr "合作伙伴关系和资助项目"

msgid "Leadership and skills development"
msgstr "领导力和技能发展"

msgid "Need Support?"
msgstr "需要支持？"

msgid "Contact us today and our team will connect you with the right service for your situation."
msgstr "立即联系我们，我们的团队将为您的情况匹配合适的服务。"

