msgstr "真实影响"

msgid "Community Voices"
msgstr "社区之声"

msgid "Stories of Lives Changed"
msgstr "改变生命的故事"

msgid "Every story here represents a real person whose life was touched by the support of WMAA and our community partners. These are stories of resilience, courage, and hope."
msgstr "这里的每个故事都代表一个真实的人，他们的生活因WMAA和我们社区合作伙伴的支持而改变。这些是关于坚韧、勇气和希望的故事。"

