msgstr "简述WMAA如何在困难时期为社区成员提供支持。"

msgid "Read Full Story"
msgstr "阅读完整故事"

msgid "A brief description of how cultural mediation helped a family navigate challenges."
msgstr "简述文化调解如何帮助家庭克服挑战。"

msgid "Housing Support"
msgstr "住房支持"

msgid "A brief description of how WMAA connected a family with safe accommodation."
msgstr "简述WMAA如何帮助家庭找到安全住所。"

msgid "Fraud Prevention"
msgstr "防诈骗"

msgid "How a community member avoided a serious scam thanks to WMAA's awareness programs."
msgstr "一名社区成员如何借助WMAA的意识提升项目避免了严重诈骗。"

msgid "How WMAA helped a community member navigate the healthcare system and access vital treatment."
msgstr "WMAA如何帮助社区成员了解医疗系统并获得重要治疗。"

msgid "A story of community resilience and how WMAA's network came together to support a family in need."
msgstr "一个关于社区韧性的故事，讲述WMAA的网络如何共同支持一个有需要的家庭。"

msgid "Help Us Create More Stories Like These"
msgstr "帮助我们创造更多这样的故事"

msgid "Your support enables us to reach more people and make a real difference in our community."
msgstr "您的支持使我们能够帮助更多人，在社区中产生真实的改变。"

